		<span style="font-family:arial;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;">New Doom III Screenshots</span><span class="small">&nbsp;&nbsp;by G.Bloke at 00:34:04 GMT</span>
	</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td valign="middle">
		<p>You have to wonder whats going through the mind of these corporate press gurus when they deliberately restrict the amount of information about an upcoming game. When they have what is already billed as the game of the year, why are their press releases so lean and why isn&#39;t there an official Doom III website yet? Answers on a postcard please....
<br>
<br>Anyway, these screenshots were released apparently as part of the advertising campaign, the heads-up came from three different sites simultaneously so I&#39;ll credit them all <a href="http://www.shacknews.com/" target="_BLANK" class="pagelink">Shacknews</a> , <a href="http://www.bluesnews.com/" target="_BLANK" class="pagelink">Blues News</a> and <a href="http://3dactionplanet.com/doom/" target="_BLANK" class="pagelink">The Phobos Labs</a>.
<br>
<br><a href="https://assets.aq2world.com/archive/websites/www.actiongames.co.uk/screenshots/doom3_1.jpg" target="_BLANK" class="pagelink"><img src="https://assets.aq2world.com/archive/websites/www.actiongames.co.uk/screenshots/sm_doom3_1.jpg" alt="Actiongames News" border="0"></a> <a href="https://assets.aq2world.com/archive/websites/www.actiongames.co.uk/screenshots/doom3_2.jpg" target="_BLANK" class="pagelink"><img src="https://assets.aq2world.com/archive/websites/www.actiongames.co.uk/screenshots/sm_doom3_2.jpg" alt="Actiongames News" border="0"></a></p>
